data.description: Come live your best life in the sought after gated community of Willow Haven.  This 4 story beauty provides so much living space, beginning with a warm and inviting living room on the entry level. Soaring vaulted ceilings and large windows create a light and airy atmosphere while the stunning laminate wood flooring adds a touch of charm. A flex space on the 2nd level can be used to suit your needs - a dining room, workspace, play room - the choice is yours! Travel onward and upward to the heart of the home where you will find the kitchen and family room that showcases a fireplace and an open concept floor plan. The kitchen features an abundance of crisp, white cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and recessed lighting. Continue up to the very top level where you will find all three bedrooms,  two full bathrooms and the laundry room - yes, no carrying laundry up and down stairs for you! The attached two car garage makes parking a breeze.  The community itself has plenty of parking for guests too! Entertain on the front patio and warmly greet your neighbors as they pass by.  Willow Haven offers its residents a sparkling pool, spa and playground.   A commuter's delight being close to the 215 freeway, Kaiser/Loma Linda Hospitals and only minutes to grocery stores, dining, shopping and entertainment venues.  What are you waiting for? Don’t let this opportunity pass you by!
